From c9d2de836ce5b4783ecb1b4d1f0377e860bd13bc Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date: Sun, 31 May 2026 23:53:26 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] feat(events): revamp filters to luxury concierge taxonomy
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Replace genre-based filters (Hip-Hop, Afrobeats, Latin) and access
actions (VIP Tables, After Hours) with universal discovery filters:
All, Tonight, This Weekend, Most Wanted, Guest List, Rooftops,
Lounges, Late Night, Premium.

Re-tag all 16 events across 6 cities with new cats (mostwanted,
lounge, latenight, premium). Remove hiphop, afrobeats, latin, vip,
afterhours from all event data. Update hero subtitle copy.

No JS function changes. Filter system is data-driven — only cats
arrays and button labels updated.
---
 events.html | 49 ++++++++++++++++++++++++-------------------------
 1 file changed, 24 insertions(+), 25 deletions(-)

diff --git a/events.html b/events.html
index d410dcb..f9d5e6d 100644
